item.title: Georgia
item.description: hike from Mestia to Ushguli Tbilisi Kutaisi Batumi Stepantsminda Signagi Georgia is pretty small so you can either rent a car or download an app and hire a driver (it’s pretty cheap) who will drive you everywhere. Bus tour of the Georgian wine country around Signagi and it was amazing...
